
--------------------------------------------
Networking Library
--------------------------------------------
{DOCPATH}

1. Networking Library allows to setup network channels using channels configuration from manifest file and it's based on channel alias names accessible runtime via readir function; Using of networking library allows to setup networking channels set just use dynamical channel aliases from configuration, that way eliminates most of hardcoded data;
2. Object files belongs to this library are resides on libnetworking.a, so use:
LDFLAGS+=-lnetworking
3. Examples of usage by samples: disort, reqrep, wordcount
